						               													<description>The Sable Scourge is a semi-cooperative game played on an open world map. Players will use their turns to investigate areas of interest and stop the Sable Scourge and her henchmen from tearing up Bright City. Preventing these events and stopping the evil-doers can extend the game and give you more time to prepare for the final battle. Be careful though; if someone isn't at the right place at the right time, the final battle could approach faster. Use the glory you garner along the way to heal up, escape battles, and collect items. Every action can affect your renown (positive and negative), and the player with the most renown at the end is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Even though the game offer cooperation and teamwork skills, there is only one winner in the end, so don't share too much of the glory and claim all the renown for yourself to be the best hero Bright City has ever seen.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
